Weka will take you on a journey from downbeat and rock, through to techno and world inspired music.
In 2024, they released their self-titled debut album, Grains.
// CLOVA // [UK Garage // Jungle] Clova is a 21 year old producer and multi-instrumentalist based in Pōneke, Aotearoa.
Her live sets are 100% original productions that blend her inspirations from 90s rave culture and genres like UK Garage and Jungle, with her own take on dance music; live processing her violin and vocals to create new sonics using Ableton live.
// OHIMESAMA BREAKS // [Jungle] Originally hailing from Tamaki Makaurau, as the soundsystem as her homing beacon, she's found her way to share the love of heavy breaks, deep basslines and serious grooves with like minded people here in Te Whanganui o Tara.
